                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5239" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0768</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9094 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小资金撬动大并购——闻泰科技如何能“蛇吞象”并购安世半导体</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Small Capital Promotes Large M&amp;A, Industry Chain Collaboration Commits to Win-win——the Secrets of the Success of Wingtech&#39;s Acquisition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱茶芬，张韵竹，胡晶源</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">闻泰科技</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购；产业链协同；并购融资；半导体行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">M&amp;A; industry chain collaboration; M&amp;A financing; semiconductor industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018年，作为移动终端ODM龙头的闻泰科技收购安世半导体，268亿元的并购规模创下了中国半导体并购的新纪录。该并购面临标的资产庞大、股权架构复杂、现金支付压力大等严峻挑战。闻泰科技分步推进并购，联合战略投资者，综合运用并购借款、海外银团借款、战略投资者注资、股份支付、配套融资等多种工具，构建合理股债结构，最终以17亿元自有资金成功撬动大并购。良好的产业前景和产业链协同是此次并购成功的基础，创新的融资筹划则是并购成功的关键。通过并购，闻泰市值从194亿元跃升为1500多亿元，实现了产业升级和市值暴涨。案例为“蛇吞象”式并购如何运作、公司如何善用并购实现战略转型提供了重要启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2018, Wingtech, the top original design manufacturer (ODM) of mobile terminals, acquired Nexperia. The acquisition took 26.8 billion RMB, setting a new record for M&amp;A in Chinese semiconductor industry. Though it was confronted with severe challenges such as huge M&amp;A scale, complicated shareholding structure, and heavy cash payment pressure. Wingtech promoted the acquisition step by step and united strategic investors, as well as constructing a reasonable equity and debt structure by comprehensively utilizing a variety of financing tools such as M&amp;A loans, international syndicate loans, strategic investment, share-based payment, etc. The acquirer, in the end, successfully leveraged the acquisition with 1.7 billion RMB of its own capital. Good industrial prospects and industry chain collaboration were the basis of the success of this acquisition. And innovative financing design was the key to the success. Through the acquisition, the market value of Wingtech jumped from 19.4 billion RMB to more than 150 billion RMB, realizing industrial upgrading and market value soaring. The case provided important enlightenment on how the “snake swallowing elephant” M&amp;A works and how the company makes good use of M&amp;A to achieve strategic transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购》、《公司财务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重大并购、并购融资</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-03</td>
                            </tr>
